The issue has been resolved . Something you need to specify in the documentation is about packaging Web assembly while building ReactJS and electron applications . The *.wasm files do not get bundled .

I fixed my error in bundling the *.wasm files for build production by setting ort.env.wasm.wasmpaths overide .
